httpd(8) will also need to have libpthread.so preloaded, you can add this
to /etc/login.conf and restart with /etc/rc.d/httpd restart:

httpd:\
        :setenv=LD_PRELOAD=/usr/lib/libpthread.so:\
        :tc=daemon:
